// notify :  ValleyCallback
// all notify return NSDictionary, like
// event --  event == EVTID. To get the params;
// code  --  response error code. Right is ERR_SUCCEED
// index --  channel index. To confirm the channel
// default is string, other is int or int64. all code type(int)

// EVTID
// RTC_EVTID_RESP_LOGINED, params: index, code, event, userid
